<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Credit earned by examination is recorded without letter grade and is not computed in the overall GPA.  Credits may not be earned in courses that students previously failed.  Students may attempt to earn credit by examination in a particular course only once.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.subr.edu/index.cfm/page/115/n/654" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
